<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>About — InternLink</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
<style>
* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif; background: #fff; color: #111827; }
.page-hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg,#1e3a8a,#1d4ed8); padding: 56px 60px; text-align: center; }
.page-hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.page-hero p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 1rem; max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.7; }
.section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 64px 40px; }
.section-tag { display: inline-block; background: #eff6ff; color: #2563eb; padding: 4px 14px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.section-title { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 14px; padding: 32px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.card h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.card p { color: #374151; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.values-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 20px; margin-top: 8px; }
.value-item { text-align: center; padding: 20px; background: #f9fafb; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
.value-item .icon { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.value-item h3 { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.value-item p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #6b7280; }
.cta-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-top: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.btn-primary { background: #2563eb; color: #fff; padding: 11px 24px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; }
.btn-primary:hover { background: #1d4ed8; }
.btn-ghost { background: #f3f4f6; color: #374151; padding: 11px 24px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }
.btn-ghost:hover { background: #e5e7eb; }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .page-hero { padding: 40px 20px; } .section { padding: 48px 20px; } .values-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>
<div class="page-hero">
  <h1>About InternLink</h1>
  <p>Ethiopia's premier platform connecting university students with industry partners for meaningful internship experiences.</p>
</div>
<div class="section">
  <div class="card">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>InternLink was founded to bridge the gap between Ethiopian universities and industry, creating structured pathways for students to gain real-world experience before graduation.</p>
    <p>We believe every Ethiopian student deserves access to quality internship opportunities, and every company deserves access to talented, motivated young professionals.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h2>What We Do</h2>
    <p><strong>Admin Portal</strong> — Full management dashboard for universities and administrators to oversee the entire internship lifecycle, from student registration to performance evaluation.</p>
    <p><strong>Public Website</strong> — An open-access interface where students can browse internship opportunities and learn about partner companies.</p>
    <p><strong>Student Portal</strong> — A personalized dashboard where students can apply for internships, track application status, and communicate with supervisors.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h2>Our Values</h2>
    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-item"><div class="icon">🤝</div><h3>Collaboration</h3><p>Fostering partnerships between academia and industry.</p></div>
      <div class="value-item"><div class="icon">🔒</div><h3>Integrity</h3><p>Transparent processes and honest communication.</p></div>
      <div class="value-item"><div class="icon">🚀</div><h3>Innovation</h3><p>Continuously improving the internship experience.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cta-row">
    <a href="/public/internships" class="btn-primary">Browse Internships</a>
    <a href="/public/contact" class="btn-ghost">Contact Us</a>
  </div>
</div>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
